Recommends: pipewire-pulse | pulseaudio
Description: Terminal-based internet radio player with audio visualization
 AetherTune is a terminal-based internet radio player with real-time
 audio visualization, built in Rust. Features include a TUI interface,
 audio spectrum visualizer, world map display, and configurable stations.